parameters: \n<Male voice a>"The woman has escaped! Chase her down!!"
\n<Male voice b>"This way! She went this way! Don't let her get away!"
\n<Man's voice>"The woman is heading towards the storage room! Hurry up!"

\n<Roselitte>"...We don't have time to rest. Just a little longer, keep
it up."

\n<Ameria>"Over there, that's our stuff! Roselitte-san's sword is
there too!"
\n<Roselitte>"With that... and surely Lord Yuri's ring as well..."
\n<Thief a>"Found them! You're not getting away this time!"
\n<Thief b>"It's a pincer attack! Capture them now!"

\n<Ameria>"Ahh... let's just give up on the baggage! If we don't,
we'll get caught again!"

\n<Roselitte>"...Either way, escaping from here without proper equipment
will be difficult. And--"
\n<Roselitte>"I cannot leave Lord Yuri's ring in a place like this!"
\n<Thief c>"Wha... She broke through the iron bars...!"
\n<Thief d>"Don't be scared! We can handle this with numbers!"
\n<Ameria>"Thank goodness... my book is here too!"

\n<Thief b>"Stupid woman. To think she'd come to a place with no escape
on her own!"
\n<Thief c>"Don't expect any mercy now, brace yourself!"

\n<Roselitte>"I'll return those words to you. For all the foolish acts
you've inflicted upon me... pay with your life."

\n<Ameria>"No... I won't! I can fight too! I won't let Roselitte-san
fight alone!"
\n<Thief a>"Let's go, everyone! Let's make them suffer!"
\n<Ameria>"Ah... I'm sorry for acting on my own..."

\n<Roselitte>"Civilians should not be made to fight. From now on, stay
hidden behind me. Understood?"

parameters.name: なんとなくシリアスな感じ

parameters: Roselitte gently placed her hand on Ameria's head.
\n<Roselitte>"Thanks to you, we were saved. Um... Hallelujah?"
Ameria took out a diary from her bosom.
\n<Ameria>"...In the past, a knight saved my life."

\n<Ameria>"After that, the priest healed my injuries. That's why I
aspired to become a medical practitioner like the priest."

\n<Ameria>"I want to save people who are hurt. I want to become a
respectable medical practitioner... That's what I've been
thinking, and I've studied a lot for it."

\n<Ameria>"...That's why I want to help Roselitte-san. I want to be of
use."

\n<Ameria>"I'll do my best not to be a burden. Please let me fight
alongside you."
\n<Roselitte>"...As I've said many times, you are--"

\n<Ameria>"Yes. I'm not a soldier. But I'm not just a civilian
either."

\n<Ameria>"I am a medical practitioner. And I'm the doctor who
promised to take care of Roselitte-san."

\n<Ameria>"I can't just stand by silently and let an injured person
fight. I can't do such a thing."
Ameria looked straight into Roselitte's eyes.
\n<Ameria>"I have a responsibility to help Roselitte-san."
\n<Ameria>"No matter what you say, I will fight alongside you."
\n<Roselitte>"...It seems that no matter what I say, it will be in vain."

\n<Roselitte>"However, do not act recklessly. You must follow my
instructions at all times. And you may accompany me only
until we reach a safe place.... Understood?"
\n<Ameria>"I look forward to working with you! Roselitte-san!"
\n<Roselitte>"...Yes. I look forward to working with you as well."
